        "default": "<p>Use manual mode to tailor your vibrator intensity, patterns, and vibrations as per your preference. Or, choose the automatic mode to seamlessly synchronize your device with the progression of the erotic audio storyline. We've created an experience that you can feel and hear.</p>"
    }
  ],
  "blocks": [
